snippet.title: Rittenhouse: TYT, Ana Kasparian on ASU Student Protest | Bad Faith, Kyle Kulinski, Useful Idiots
snippet.description:
In this video, Kam and Sam discuss:

- 04:35 Kyle Rittenhouse 
- 55:50 Bad Faith Interviews 
- 01:42:00 Kyle Kulinski 
- 02:03:10 Geopolitical Briefs 
- 02:03:12 Iran Nuclear Talks Resume 
- 02:40:20 Russiagate Continues 
- 03:00:00 Lego gives its 20,000 employees three days extra holiday after profits rise 140%

Spar&Brawl. is a news and politics show co-hosted by Kam in the red corner and Sam in the blue corner. They discuss and debate some of the biggest — and least covered — news stories from around the world. As friends and sparring partners, they always promise to go light, but every now and then, a good old-fashioned brawl breaks out.
